ignment, cybersecurity boundaries, disaster recovery, and model failovers to guarantee compliance.\"\n 96 |             badge=\"Index 03\"\n 97 |             icon={<CheckSquare className=\"w-5 h-5 text-purple-400\" />}\n 98 |             glowColor=\"purple\"\n 99 |           />\n100 |         </BentoGrid>\n101 |       </div>\n102 | \n103 |       <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-16 py-12\">\n104 |         <h2 className=\"text-[28px] sm:text-[34px] font-bold text-white tracking-tight mb-4\">\n105 |           Publications & Whitepaper Library\n106 |         </h2>\n107 |         <p className=\"text-[15px] text-white/60 max-w-[700px] mb-8 font-light\">\n108 |           Download our technical research papers and architectural specifications.\n109 |         </p>\n110 | \n111 |         <ResearchLibraryGrid />\n112 |       </div>\n113 | \n114 |       <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-16 py-16 flex flex-col gap-16\">\n115 |         <PremiumCTA\n116 |           title=\"Elevate Your Corporate Governance\"\n117 |           description=\"Schedule a technical deep-dive with our quantitative research division to audit and evaluate your organization.\"\n118 |         />\n119 | \n120 |         <RelatedPagesGrid links={filteredLinks} />\n121 |       </div>\n122 |     </InnerPageShell>\n123 |   );\n124 | }","success":true}],"durationMs":2}}
